metadata.title: 1981 U.S. Sablefish Tagging Survey

creators.name: Atmospheric Administration (NOAA), National Marine Fisheries Service (NMFS), Alaska Fisheries Science Center (AFSC)

metadata.description: Alaska sablefish tagging data, consisting of release and recovery sizes and the length of time fish were at liberty, provide an independent estimate of growth rates.  The vessel was named ISIS (USA).
metadata.notes:
Purpose: Primarily to provide resource assessment estimates to management.
